Good day <%= @recipient_name %>

We are thrilled to hear that <%= @block.name %> is considering an organic waste service for its
residents. What a wonderful step forward in sustainability.

We have quite a bit of experience in setting these systems up and would love to work with you
to make it a reality.

I have put together a short presentation you can share with your group of trustees, as well as a
