  <%= @survey_url %>

A note on the phased approach: In our experience it is unlikely that all residents adopt the
practice immediately. We can run the rollout in phases so you are not paying for processing
volume that isn't being used. The resident survey helps us understand who is ready to start
immediately and whether they need a countertop bucket. Based on the results we may find half
the estate is ready to go, with the rest joining after the initial 6 month subscription.

If you have any questions or would like to have a call to discuss, please feel free to let me know.

Looking forward to hearing from you.

